## Benchmark Performance / 基准测试性能（mAP@0.5）

| Model | mAP | FPS (A40) | 中文模型名 | mAP | FPS |
|-------|-----|-----------|------------|-----|-----|
| YOLOv12 | **0.889** | 80 | YOLOv12 | **0.889** | 80 |
| YOLOv10 | 0.871 | 77 | YOLOv10 | 0.871 | 77 |
| YOLOv11 | 0.873 | 49 | YOLOv11 | 0.873 | 49 |
| YOLOv8 | 0.867 | 63 | YOLOv8 | 0.867 | 63 |
| YOLOv5 | 0.861 | 47 | YOLOv5 | 0.861 | 47 |
| RT-DETR | 0.834 | 42 | RT-DETR | 0.834 | 42 |

**English:** YOLOv12 achieves the best overall performance. Our experiments also show excellent cross-dataset generalization when training on MASS-LSVD.  
**中文：** YOLOv12 取得最佳整体性能。跨数据集实验表明，使用 MASS-LSVD 训练的模型具有良好的泛化能力。

