## Dataset Access / 数据集获取--部分 A Part

**English:** Download the dataset from the GitHub repository:  
**中文：** 数据集下载地址：Please send e-mail to :dmuusv@163.com

📦 [https://github.com/lcolorworker/MASS-LSVD-A-Large-Scale-First-View-Dataset-for-VesselDetection](https://github.com/lcolorworker/MASS-LSVD-A-Large-Scale-First-View-Dataset-for-VesselDetection)

**English:** The dataset includes all images, annotation files (COCO format), and a train/test split (8:2).  
**中文：** 数据集中包含全部图像、COCO 格式标注文件以及 8:2 训练/测试划分。

